@CarRental.API_HostAddress = https://localhost:7174
@AuthToken = your_jwt_token_here

### ============================================
### CATEGORIES
### ============================================

### Get all categories
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/categories
Accept: application/json

###

### Get category by ID
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/categories/1
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================
### CARS
### ============================================

### Get all cars (default pagination)
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/cars
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all cars with filters
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/cars?categoryId=1&fuel=Petrol&minPrice=100&maxPrice=500&page=1&pageSize=5&sortBy=price&sortDirection=asc
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all cars filtered by brand
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/cars?brand=Toyota
Accept: application/json

###

### Get car by ID
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/cars/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new car
POST {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/cars
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 2,
  "brand": "Toyota",
  "model": "Corolla",
  "year": 2024,
  "regNr": "ABC-123",
  "fuel": "Petrol",
  "transmission": "Automatic",
  "seats": 5,
  "price": 250.00,
  "status": "Available"
}

###

### Update a car
PUT {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/cars/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 2,
  "brand": "Toyota",
  "model": "Corolla",
  "year": 2024,
  "regNr": "ABC-123",
  "fuel": "Petrol",
  "transmission": "Automatic",
  "seats": 5,
  "price": 275.00,
  "status": "Available"
}

###

### Delete a car
DELETE {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/cars/1

###

### ============================================
### CUSTOMERS
### ============================================

### Register a new customer
POST {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phone": "+46701234567",
  "address": "123 Main Street",
  "city": "Stockholm",
  "postalCode": "11122",
  "country": "Sweden"
}

###

### Get customer by ID
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/customers/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Update customer profile
PUT {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phone": "+46709876543",
  "address": "456 New Street",
  "city": "Gothenburg",
  "postalCode": "41101",
  "country": "Sweden"
}

###

### ============================================
### RENTALS (PHASE 4)
### ============================================

### Check car availability
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/rentals/availability?carId=1&startDate=2026-03-10T10:00:00&endDate=2026-03-15T10:00:00
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new rental booking
POST {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/rentals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "carId": 1,
  "startDate": "2026-03-10T10:00:00",
  "endDate": "2026-03-15T10:00:00"
}

###

### Get rental by ID
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/rentals/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Get my rentals (customer)
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/rentals/my-rentals?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Get all rentals (admin only)
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/rentals?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Update rental status (admin only)
PUT {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/rentals/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "status": "Confirmed"
}

###

### Cancel a rental
DELETE {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/rentals/1
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### ============================================
### ADMIN
### ============================================

### Get dashboard statistics
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/admin/stats
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all customers (admin)
GET {{CarRental.API_HostAddress}}/admin/customers
Accept: application/json

###

